\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Duck_Mayonnaise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Duck Mayonnaise is used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> with <a href=\"/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">Cloth</a> in the feed to create an <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Shirt009.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Shirt009.png/24px-Shirt009.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/8/8a/Shirt009.png 1.5x\" /> <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Aquamarine Shirt</a></span>. It is a white dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Duck_Mayonnaise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Duck Mayonnaise is not used in any <a href=\"/Quests\" title=\"Quests\">quests</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Secrets\">Secrets</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Duck_Mayonnaise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Secrets\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>If Duck Mayonnaise is placed in the partially-hidden purple box in the back room of the <a href=\"/The_Stardrop_Saloon\" title=\"The Stardrop Saloon\">The Stardrop Saloon</a>, the player will receive the <a href=\"/File:%3F%3FPinky_Lemon%3F%3F.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"??Pinky Lemon??.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/37/%3F%3FPinky_Lemon%3F%3F.png/16px-%3F%3FPinky_Lemon%3F%3F.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"16\" height=\"32\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/37/%3F%3FPinky_Lemon%3F%3F.png/24px-%3F%3FPinky_Lemon%3F%3F.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/3/37/%3F%3FPinky_Lemon%3F%3F.png/32px-%3F%3FPinky_Lemon%3F%3F.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/%3F%3FPinky_Lemon%3F%3F\" title=\"??Pinky Lemon??\">??Pinky Lemon??</a> statue.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Duck_Mayonnaise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.0\" title=\"Version History\">1.0</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.1\" title=\"Version History\">1.1</a>: Increased value from 300g to 375g.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Can now be used in <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</a>.  Fixed bug where an entire stack of Duck Mayonnaise would be consumed when interacting with the box in the Saloon.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Duck Mayonnaise can now be consumed.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Artisan_Goods\" title=\"Artisan Goods\">Artisan Goods</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Bee_House\" title=\"Bee House\">Bee House</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Mead\" title=\"Mead\"