      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Duck Mayonnaise\n|source      = [[Artisan Goods]]\n|ingredients = {{Name|Duck Egg|1}}\n|sellprice   = 375\n|edibility   = 30\n|crafttime   = 3h\n|craftingstation = {{Name|Mayonnaise Machine}}\n|quality     = false\n}}\n'''Duck Mayonnaise''' is an [[Artisan Goods|Artisan Good]] made by placing a [[Duck Egg]] into a [[Mayonnaise Machine]], taking 3 hours.\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|like=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Linus,Pierre,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jodi,Kent,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus,Leo\n|hate=Sebastian,Jas,Vincent,Sam\n|dislike=Caroline\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nDuck Mayonnaise is not used in any [[Bundles|bundles]].\n\n==Recipes==\nDuck Mayonnaise is not used in any recipes.\n\n==Tailoring==\nDuck Mayonnaise is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create an {{Name|Shirt009|link=Tailoring{{!}}Aquamarine Shirt|class=inline}}. It is a white dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed.\n\n==Quests==\nDuck Mayonnaise is not used in any [[Quests|quests]].\n\n==Secrets==\nIf Duck Mayonnaise is placed in the partially-hidden purple box in the back room of the [[The Stardrop Saloon]], the player will receive the [[File:??Pinky Lemon??.png|16px]] [[??Pinky Lemon??]] statue.\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.1|Increased value from 300g to 375g.}}\n{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].  Fixed bug where an entire stack of Duck Mayonnaise would be consumed when interacting with the box in the Saloon.}}\n{{History|1.6|Duck Mayonnaise can now be consumed.}}\n\n{{NavboxArtisanGoods}}\n\n[[Category:Artisan Goods]]\n\n[[de:Enten-Mayonnaise]]\n[[es:Mayonesa de pato]]\n[[fr:Mayonnaise de canard]]\n[[it:Maionese d'anatra]]\n[[ja:ダックマヨネーズ]]\n[[ko:오리 마요네즈]]\n[[hu:Kacsa majonéz]]\n[[pt:Maionese de ovo de pato]]\n[[ru:Утиный майонез]]\n[[tr:Ördek Mayonezi]]\n[[zh:鸭蛋黄酱]]"
